olá, érika, boa tarde!! ‌ agradecemos pelo envio do seu currículo e pelo seu interesse em fazer parte da nossa equipe. ‌ recebemos suas informações com sucesso e, caso seu perfil esteja alinhado com as necessidades da posição em aberto, entraremos em contato para darmos continuidade ao processo seletivo. ‌ desejamos sucesso em sua trajetória profissional. ‌ atenciosamente,

service lat is responsible for ensuring the best performance possible of wind turbines in the lat sub (latin america). the position will be part of the service analytics from operations service department. ‌ responsibilities: - develop visual tools such as power bi to create a clear picture for management and ensure stakeholders are informed on continuous basis on how they are performing and trending - update and do maintenance on dashboards (power bi) already available in lat sbu - perform data analysis to find cost-out opportunities/initiatives through entire service value chain in all latin america service organization - do process automation regarding data collection, data transformation and data modeling in order to support on the digital transformation ‌ qualifications: ‌ - bachelors degree in it or correlated areas (engineer, statistics etc) - proficient knowledge in etl process and data modelling, web scraping is a plus - extensive knowledge in database (e.g., data lake, data warehouse) - advanced skills on power bi tool - experience with power automate and power apps - proficient in microsoft office programs (power point, excel, word) - extensive knowledge in python, sql (power shell) - desired experience with sap, salesforce objects - desired experience with app development - desired knowledge in machine learning - knowledge in machine learning - proficiency in english and spanish (desired) - good investigative skills including the ability to evaluate and interpret complex information from numerous sources, prepare and present analysis and reports, deal with issues creatively and find business-focused solutions - good organizational skills and experience working in a high volume and inspiring professional environment with a capacity to prioritize, manage multiple responsibilities, reach business goals, perform, and always work with a customer-focused approach ‌ ‌ location: natal

[click here to take the 1-minute timed test.](https://somewheretypingtest.com/test "‌") ![📌](https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/e/notoemoji/16.0/1f4cc/32.png) if you experience any technical issues preventing you from completing the test, please send proof to [help@somewhere.com](mailto:help@somewhere.com "‌"), and we will review your request accordingly. ‌ \_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\__ ![ad\_4nxfkznlpvvq4psde9t2jbqkyadtaiav\_szxtxuzvan-plcnl-lwvx0jtiqf088whjnscmdduobyp\_s215kjl2fgow-uj9cmpuzlacevbhgoujwopapwy35knzjl95uwmhzxecbxfhfge23\_lbe8vbj2wx4dew6w\_xypecjdmda?key=f22hx3hrgif7y5mjxzfvkq](https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/ad_4nxfkznlpvvq4psde9t2jbqkyadtaiav_szxtxuzvan-plcnl-lwvx0jtiqf088whjnscmdduobyp_s215kjl2fgow-uj9cmpuzlacevbhgoujwopapwy35knzjl95uwmhzxecbxfhfge23_lbe8vbj2wx4dew6w_xypecjdmda?key=f22hx3hrgif7y5mjxzfvkq) max mwape senior recruiter

‌ erika, você está dentro do nosso processo seletivo! ‌ a primeira etapa já está disponível para você na plataforma! pedimos para que acesse o link abaixo em até 2 dias, para realizá-la. [https://looqbox.gupy.io/candidates/applications/585803218](https://email.gupy.com.br/c/ejwcjufurtamae-t7d5kdnhmkcxfca-thbivcap5vd_tk7ocatstwroyera5ebrby8_edgs4rupthaijii2uhs4dere4pglwwwi4gb1559f7t93egvecwhbjirkywx286rulentlzfewtvzv0_83mbuyd9wvrx-6p6eogtnkmuqslm8ds9s6lyit6pngyco7hjzbk-srfmqtcux7mipbtb1s9udjw4h6vdnf_wbhclafeml6xsdjvwp8bgaa__-vvejq "‌") nesta primeira etapa, queremos que você grave um áudio (até 60 segundos) respondendo a seguinte pergunta: - conte-nos algum desafio na programação que você tem orgulho de ter resolvido, e como você fez para resolvê-lo. queremos que você foque somente no conteúdo da sua resposta, deixando de lado qualquer preocupação com a imagem. o nosso foco está em ouvir a sua resposta! por isso, pedimos para você tapar sua câmera. a plataforma não possui a função de desabilitar a câmera, por isso, siga nosso passo-a-passo antes de responder a pergunta: 1. tape sua câmera: use um pedaço de papel, pano, ou de fita adesiva, o que preferir! você pode, inclusive, redirecionar sua câmera para uma parede. 1. clique em _“gravar novo vídeo”_ no meio da página_._ 1. libere o acesso à câmera e microfone na janela que irá aparecer no canto superior esquerdo da tela clicando em _“permitir”._ a câmera deve permanecer tapada. 1. clique no círculo vermelho no meio da tela para começar a gravar a sua resposta. aguarde a contagem regressiva para iniciar. 1. quando finalizar, é só clicar no mesmo círculo vermelho novamente. 1. assista a gravação e, se estiver contente, clique em “_utilizar vídeo”_. caso queira refazer, clique em _“gravar novamente”_. 1. após a plataforma processar sua resposta, você poderá rever a gravação e, se desejar, excluir o arquivo e regravar clicando em _“gravar novo vídeo”._ se estiver feliz com o resultado, clique em _“enviar para empresa”_ para finalizar. se preferir, a plataforma disponibiliza a opção de subir um arquivo nos formatos: mp4 e webm. ‌ aproveite para conhecer um pouco mais do looqbox em nosso material em anexo: por dentro do looqbox. prepare-se e boa sorte! ‌ atenciosamente, jaqueline torres time people & culture

job id 309487date posted 06/03/2025location : uberlândia, brazilcategory digital technology and data (dt&d)job status salaried full time want to build a stronger, more sustainable future and cultivate your career? join cargills global team of 160,000 employees who use new technologies, dynamic insights and over 154 years of experience to connect farmers with markets, customers with ingredients, and people and animals with the food they need to thrive.  job purpose the data analyst will develop an in depth understanding of the business to innovate significant data driven insights to help business leaders make better decisions and will develop and combine subject matter expertise in key data domains. in this role, you will act as a partner with internal stakeholders and technical staff to execute a business technology strategy that delivers reporting and analytics solutions for cargill’s transportation & procurement.  accountabilities - reporting & visualization: identify and analyze business needs, gather requirements and define the scope and objectives to drive business decisions. - data collection & analysis: prepare data and explore new potential data to support reporting and analysis initiatives, including data ingestion processes. - statistical analysis: prepare reports and analytical products to identify, analyze and interpret trends or patterns in complex data sets for values and new opportunities. - process improvement: lead analysis in collaboration with process and operations leadership to identify the top opportunities for improvement and track progress and impact on future results. - collaboration: partner with the team to develop a detailed understanding of the business and offer mentorship or technical solutions to identify business problems. - other duties as assigned  qualifications - bachelor’s degree in a related field or equivalent experience - confirmed skills querying relational databases with query language - confirmed experience working with large data stores - proficiency with sql, python, and/or tableau/power bi - experience in agile product delivery model - experience querying database management systems preferred - experience with transportation and/or procurement data - functional knowledge of technology systems, including sap -
